Package app

Class NetExchangeTestConstants

java.lang.Object
app.NetExchangeTestConstants
public final class NetExchangeTestConstants extends Object
Defines constants shared by the network exchange and proxy test drivers. If the properties are defined they override the default values.
Author:
Russ Moul
